beadID string, op func() error) error.\u0026#xA;2. handleOutcomeStoreError deleted from execute_bead_loop.go.\u0026#xA;3. All 14 callsites in execute_bead_loop.go (pre-refactor: 628, 740, 763, 800, 834, 850, 869, 877, 905, 918, 963, 979, 1014, 1026) replaced with commitOutcome.\u0026#xA;4. TestCommitOutcome_StoreErrorContinuesLoop verifies that a store write failure schedules cooldown and returns nil (loop continues).\u0026#xA;5. TestCommitOutcome_StoreError_SchedulesCooldown_NotExit verifies cooldown event is recorded with ParkReason=loop-error.\u0026#xA;6. C0 fixture diff: store-glitch-during-close lifecycle byte-identical event stream (loop-error event present, no hard exit).\u0026#xA;7. cd cli \u0026amp;\u0026amp; go test ./internal/agent/... green.\u0026#xA;8. lefthook run pre-commit passes.\n    \u003c/acceptance\u003e\n    \u003clabels\u003ephase:2, refactor, kind:refactor\u003c/labels\u003e\n    \u003cmetadata parent=\"ddx-5cb6e6cd\" base-rev=\"d538e5a4e2cd461d905096cc26160f238c2bf198\" bundle=\".ddx/executions/20260506T005446-0d4a0770\"/\u003e\n  \u003c/bead\u003e\n  \u003cgoverning\u003e\n    \u003cnote\u003eNo governing references were pre-resolved. The bead description above is the primary contract. If it names files, specs, or prior beads, read those before editing. Ground decisions in what is already in the repository; do not guess.\u003c/note\u003e\n  \u003c/governing\u003e\n\u003c/execute-bead\u003e\n","metadata":{"attempt_id":"20260506T005446-0d4a0770","base_rev":"d538e5a4e2cd461d905096cc26160f238c2bf198","bead_id":"ddx-b669bb9f","bundle_path":".ddx/executions/20260506T005446-0d4a0770","correlation_id":"ddx-b669bb9f:20260506T005446-0d4a0770","prompt_file":".ddx/executions/20260506T005446-0d4a0770/prompt.md","prompt_sha":"9c26c9f0bcca88d98a8748b81310b578121640fdf8fc1e29da84f3535bc56520","role":"implementer","session_id":"eb-7bd64327","worker_id":""}}}
